snippet.title: Final Fantasy XVI Trailer | The Game Awards 2022
snippet.description: Naoki Yoshida took the stage at the 2022 Game Awards to show an all new epic trailer for Final Fantasy XVI, showing confident combat, remarkable environments, and impressive monsters to fight. Final Fantasy XVI is exclusive to the PS5.
